	('students', 'Students', 'Our vision is "PALS" — a mixture of Greek and English words. P-phronesis (wisdom/prudence), A-agape (sacrificial love), L-logos (word/truth), S-service/dedication. We help students mature in PALS through weekly small groups, special workshops, and church-related volunteering opportunities with brothers and sisters in small group community.', '{david-kao}', '{}', false);
